SUMMARY:Mike Glazer Stand-Up Comedy Live @ The Melon Ball
DESCRIPTION:Watermelon Music in Davis presents Mike Glazer. \nWhen Kanye West shared Mike Glazer’s joke\, he thought his life was about to change. And it did\, in the worst way imaginable\, until Taylor Swift’s Swifties saved his life.\nMike Glazer is chaotic good: a twisted\, endearing storyteller like an evil Mike Birbiglia. He wishes the following weren’t true\, but he has the receipts to prove it — before becoming a comedian\, Glazer was a strip-club–sponsored roller hockey goalie who almost became an Olympian\, nearly became an astronaut for British royal billionaires\, shared his phone number with the entire world in a horribly stupid prank\, and somehow became the CIA for a month\, which sucked.\nIf you’ve ever wanted to hear the words\, “so the Swifties were battling the Nazis\,” come to this show. As Kanye said\, “it’s good deal.”\n$15 General Admission\nDoors open at 7:30pm\nThis is a BYOB Event!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/mike-glazer-stand-up-comedy-live-the-melon-ball/
LOCATION:Watermelon Music\, 1970 Lake Blvd\, DAVIS\, CA\, 95616\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Glazer_new-poster.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Watermelon Music":MAILTO:info@watermelonmusic.com
END:VEVENT
